        "subject": "LU-2642 mgs: fix missing error code return in mgs_fs_setu",
        "message": "LU-2642 mgs: fix missing error code return in mgs_fs_setu\n\nThe GOTO macro calls in mgs_fs_setup doesn't assign rc to the value\npassed to it. As a result, if dt_locate_at fails, it will return early\nbut also return instead of PTR_ERR(root) as intended.\n\nThis was caught by PTR_ERR being __must_check as of v3.6.34.\n\nSigned-off-by: Jeff Mahoney <jeffm@suse.com>\nChange-Id: Ie4897440d481980de6c4d345d2ab2120b44b32c7\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
    }
